name: Ekphrasis XXI
description: "Not in the Tall Grass" - a reaction piece about the film "In the Tall Grass", but instead of the desire for ultimate wisdom and knowledge about the universe - how about NONE of that? I want a Tree of Unknowledge. Make me forget answers I shouldn't have known. Shut my mind down! I don't want to know anymore. Leave me be, among the grass in the countryside before sundown looking up the sky, daydreaming like a child again.
